apps.title: CHEERZ - Photo Printing
apps.description:
Cheerz, making photo printing easy ! 
Order your photo prints directly from your phone: photo albums, photo prints, magnets, frames, posters... All from the comfort of your own home. Magical, isn't it ?
 
Cheerz prints the memories of over 4 million customers worldwide ! With 97% satisfaction, that's a lot of smiles, right ?

▶ PHOTO PRODUCTS TO CREATE ON OUR APP
• Photo album : Thanks to a simplified interface, create a unique photo book to put your memories on high quality paper.
• Photo prints : Between an image on a screen and a print in your hands, there’s no comparing.
• DIY photo book : It doesn’t get more personalised than this. You’ll receive a complete kit: photo prints, a pen, decorations, masking tape... to create the album of a lifetime !
• Photo box : Not just your favourite photo prints, but also a pretty box to keep them safe in.
• Memory box : A real treasure box (of photos) with a unique code to print up to 300 prints all year long.
• Photo magnets : personalised magnets to stick everywhere. The best excuse to pay the fridge a visit. 
• Posters, Frames, Canvases, Aluminum : Posters, Frames, Canvases, Aluminum, for when you can't decide between a photo or decor.
• Calendar : A nice personalised photo calendar to make you smile every day of the year !
 
Cheerz products in short : memories, photo decoration, personalised gifts... And lots and lots of "Cheerz" in every shot !
 
WHY CHEERZ ?
 
▶ AN INTERFACE WITH A SIMPLE DESIGN
The interface is designed to make each photo product a pleasure to create. The photo album is quick and easy to make.

▶ INNOVATIVE
The only app that simplifies the creation of a photo album on your smartphone !
2 possibilities : the creation of a photo book from scratch for the most creative, or using auto-fill thanks to a simple and intuitive interface. Any occasion will soon become an excuse to create a photo book...
Our R&D team are like genies, your wish is their command ! In 2 years, they’ve revolutionized the creation of photo products on mobile !

▶ TOP QUALITY AND CUSTOMER SERVICE
In all humility, our app has received 5 stars since its launch.
Our happiness team responds in less than 6 hours, including weekends.
Premium photo printing quality : printed in France on real photo paper (that means digital AND silver paper for select products).
Fast delivery and order tracking.
 
▶ ENVIRONMENTAL RESPONSIBILITY
Cheerz is committed to reducing its carbon footprint by making more responsible and environmentally friendly choices.
Our photo albums and prints are FSC certified, a label promoting responsible forest management (we even replant trees in Peru !).
 
▶ IT’S BIG IN PARIS 
The French are known for their good taste, and not just in food and fashion ! 

Why print your photos ?
Memories are sacred, and the photos on your phone deserve to be printed (rather than collect dust in your smartphone) !
 
Printing is more convenient than ever! In the blink of an eye, create quality photo products for yourself : photo books, photo prints, enlargements, posters, photo frames, boxes, photo canvases, magnets...
 
Friendly reminder, Cheerz is a gift to give for any occasion : an album of holiday memories, your last weekend with friends, a decorative frame in your new apartment... to list a few examples. 
The ideal gift at a low cost that’s sure to please ! 
See you soon,
The Cheerz team
 

---------------------------
▶ ABOUT CHEERZ
Cheerz, formerly Polabox, is a French photo printing service specialising in mobile photo printing and photos shared on social networks. Our products have quite the reputation, and they’ve been known to make our customers smile !
 
All our photo products are printed in our Cheerz Factory, a local factory based in Gennevilliers, just outside of Paris! Cheerz is an app downloaded by more than 4 million users in Europe.
 
Cheerz is on Facebook (over 500,000 fans) and on Instagram (over 300,000 followers). Trust us, we're going to make you want to print your photos.

raw_data.releaseNotes: The light fades earlier and leaves crunch underfoot: there's no doubt about it, autumn is here to stay. It's the season for long Sundays, reading under a blanket and cups of fragrant tea. And to keep up with this cocooning atmosphere, we've decided to simplify your customisation experience. Now you can enjoy albums that are easy to try, personalise and love. This autumn, printing your photos will become your new cosy ritual

apps.title: LumaBooth Event Photo Booth
apps.description:
From the creators of dslrBooth, LumaBooth is the leading professional photo booth software for iPad, iPhone, and Mac. Perfect for easily running a professional-grade photo booth and video/360 booth at weddings, birthdays, company parties, and more. Easily run a professional-grade photo booth and video/360 booth.

Photo Booth:
• Custom Layouts and Editing: Use LumaBooth's user-friendly editor to craft personalized photo layouts. Incorporate images, logos, and text effortlessly.
• Stickers and Filters: Engage your guests with a wide array of stickers, filters, and LUTs allowing them to personalize their photos for a truly interactive experience.
• Versatile Printing Options: Enjoy the flexibility of printing with any AirPrint-compatible printer or connect to professional photo printers through the LumaBooth Assistant app. Exclusive support for DNP printers via the DNP WPS Pro print server enhances your printing capabilities.

360/Video Booth:
• Capture high-quality videos and slow-motion using built-in or professional cameras.
• Customize videos by adding image overlays, animated video overlays, pre-roll and post-roll videos, and a backing soundtrack to fit your event.
• Speed up or slow down sections of the recorded video.
• Using the high frame-rate cameras in recent iPads and iPhone, you can shoot at 240fps perfect for slow-mo effects.
• Video stabilization to ensure that your slow-motion video is captured with the utmost clarity and smoothness.
• Optionally start a session by moving the iPad or iPhone.

Key Features:
• Camera Support: Capture seamlessly with built-in cameras and offers advanced compatibility with Canon, Sony and Nikon professional cameras. Optionally setup custom camera settings such as: exposure, white balance, and video stabilization.
• Live background removal: Remove your background using AI Removal or green screen, your photos and videos will be as unique as your event.
• Guest Interaction: Guide guests through the photo booth experience using video and audio prompts.
• Surveys and Disclaimers: Turn on surveys for data collection and require a disclaimer if needed.
• Start Screen Customization: Fully customize the start screen with beautiful built-in themes.
• Professional Online Gallery: Your photos and videos are hosted in a microsite per event which you can customize to fit your event theme.
• Optionally trigger using a wireless remote.

Sharing Features:
• Fully customize the start screen with beautiful built-in themes, and allow your guests to share using e-mail, SMS, Airdrop, QR code, WhatsApp, and Instagram whether online of offline.
• Streamline your photo booth by letting guests view and share photos, prints, and GIFs on another iPad using our companion LumaShare iPad app. Also run a live photo or video slideshow.


LumaBooth requires a subscription which offers unlimited events with no watermark, sharing using SMS, E-mail, Facebook, and Twitter:
• The LumaBooth monthly renewable subscription costs $19.99 USD.
• Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase.
• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period
• Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal
• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase
• No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period
• Please go to dslrbooth.com/terms-of-service/ and dslrbooth.com/privacy-policy for more information.

apps.title: Mixbook | Photo Book Creator
apps.description:
CREATIVITY MADE EASY
Get started with thousands of beautiful themes for every occasion. From family vacations, weddings, anniversaries, baby showers, birthdays, yearbooks, holidays, graduations, and more. Or, start from a blank template. Our mobile-friendly Mixbook Studio lets you design an amazing photo book in minutes, without the need for any design skills. “You can customize everything to your liking” - Good Housekeeping

EASILY TELL YOUR STORY
AI-powered features like Memories (app exclusive) and Auto-Create identify your best photos and help you start creating. Recommended Layouts automatically adjust to fit your photos, instantly transforming them into a beautiful story.  “Mixbook actually makes it fun to create photo books” - Wirecutter

PHOTO-BOOK-READY ALBUMS WITH MEMORIES
Discover forgotten moments and turn them into a story you can relive. The Mixbook app groups the photos on your camera roll into Memories. Spend less time organizing photos and more time reliving your favorite moments while you turn them into share-worthy photo books. “So incredibly easy to use” - Digital Camera World

PICTURE-PERFECT QUALITY
We want your memories to last a lifetime, so we don't skimp on quality. Easily explore our book sizes, paper types, and finishes so you get the right option for your occasion and budget. “The finish is so excellent you feel like you’ve created a work of art” - TechRadar

ONE-OF-A-KIND GIFTS FOR ALL
Create more than just books. From wall decor to cards and calendars, you can make photo gifts for any occasion on Mixbook. Perfect for family, friends, and more!

PHOTO STORAGE AND SHARING:
Your photos are safe with us, and you always have access to your photos and projects. Relive and reprint your stories as many times as you'd like. Plus, with Mixbook, you can easily share a digital copy of your photo book with friends and family. It's a great alternative to other photo sharing sites, and a wonderful way to share your memories with the people who matter.

100% HAPPINESS GUARANTEED:
At Mixbook, every team member is committed to helping our customers create their best photo book ever. We believe in our product because we love connecting with people and sharing memories. Your treasured moments are important to us. We’ll make sure you’re 100% happy every step of the way.

apps.title: Photo Album Private Manager
apps.description:
Looking for real privacy to manage your photos and videos?

Photo Album is the best photo management solution to manage your photos and videos with strong Privacy features, lots of functionalities to Organize, create Slideshows and Sync your photos and videos between devices with iCloud end-to-end encryption and Dropbox. 

Sync directly from device to device and WiFi transfer of photos from device and computer.

PRIVACY FEATURES

+ Customizable 4 digit to 10 digit passcode to login to the App.

+ Three layers of privacy with passcode, password and invisible mode for private albums.

+ Supports Face ID and Touch ID to login to the App.

+ Ultra double lock needs passcode and Face ID authentication to login.

+ Intruder Break-In report with photo, date and time. Report of all who tried to break-in to the App.

+ App access report with photo, date and time. Report of all who logged into the App.

+ PIN and Password reset option with unique secret key.

+ Turn invisible mode off just for the session to access private albums, private albums will disappear when closing the App with this option.

+ Safe share photos for secure encrypted access with iCloud link.


PHOTO MANAGEMENT FEATURES

+ Import unlimited photos, videos and GIFs into Albums, option to select all or just unsaved photos, supports background process for importing photos. 

+ Supports file sharing extension to allow importing from Photos, Files and from other Apps.

+ Sort or Move the photos(among multiple Albums) by a simple drag and drop gesture. 

+ App generated photo categories, intuitive search by photo categories and face.
 
+ Search similar photos to find duplicate and redundant photos. 

+ View photos with music in animated slideshow with 12 transition styles and effects.

+ View photo metadata with swipe up gesture on photo view screen.

+ Create wallpaper from photos in the album.

+ Listen to your favorite playlist of songs in the App with slideshows.

+ Record slideshows with animated GIFs, 12 transition styles and effects.

+ Wi-Fi Sync within App across devices and with computer using Wi-Fi drive and Web browser.

+ Backup and restore. Keep your photos and videos synced between devices with iCloud.

+ Backup and restore. Keep your photos and videos synced between devices with Dropbox.

apps.title: Motionleap: 3D Photo Animator
apps.description:
Create moving photos for a unique type of photo art! Animate your photos & magically bring them to life with Motionleap. The newest addition to the award-winning Enlight Creativity Suite of apps, brought to you by Lightricks, takes photo editing to the next level. 

Motionleap brings life to images through animation, creating moving pictures that will wow anyone from your friends to Instagram followers. Animate one element or several, drawing attention to parts of your photo that YOU want to come alive. With the same ease of use brought to you in the rest of the Enlight Creativity Suite, including Photofox, Lightleap, and Videoleap (Apple’s App of the Year), Motionleap allows you to easily edit photos with powerful, precise, and easy to use animation tools. In just a few taps animate, add elements & overlays, adjust the speed and watch your image come to life. As a result you’ll get incredible videos that boomerang back and forth or flow like a GIF. 

Need inspiration? Follow #Motionleap, then tag your own creations and we’ll feature the best ones!

Get excited about the power of Motionleap features:

ANIMATED PHOTOS MADE EASY

- Animate a photo with a few taps and swipes
- Arrows will show motion direction
- Place anchor points to hold parts of image in place
- Freeze sections of photos with a Freeze brush

AI POWERED WATER ANIMATION

- NEW automated water animation
- Effortless water movement with a single tap

FANTASTIC SKY REPLACEMENT TECHNOLOGY

- Replace bland Skies with colorful sunsets or animated clouds
- Wide variety of automated Skies resembling timelapse

HYPNOTIC GEOMETRIC MOTION

- Geometric photo animation tool creates spinning towers and umbrellas 
- Move your favorite historical landmarks in a never before seen way
- Add patterned movement to iconic buildings

VIDEO EFFECTS & OVERLAYS IN A PHOTO EDITOR

- Control movement & animation including speed, direction, and style 
- Mimic cinematic movement with Camera FX
- Camera effects & movements include Tilt, Zoom, and ‘Dolly’ effects
- Add fun Overlays to bring movement, mood, & emotion to still photos
- Distort perspective & style with effects

MOVING ELEMENTS IN STILL PHOTOS

- Grab attention with a moving element - candle flickers, coffee steam, or a butterfly
- A new kind of animation between photos, videos, and GIFs
- Add a cinemagraph effect with a moving element in a still photo

INFINITE ARTISTIC POSSIBILITY

- Animate any photo element: hair, waves, clouds & clothing
- Push your imagination with Motionleap high-end & easy animation tools
- Create moving masterpieces that serve your social media presence, business, or personal brand

apps.title: PRESETS: Filters for Pictures
apps.description:
Presets: The Ultimate Photo App for Editing Your Visuals!

Are you tired of the same old filters and effects on your photos and videos? Look no further than Presets, the revolutionary app that takes your visual editing experience to the next level. With Presets, you have access to a wide range of powerful editing tools and features that will transform your ordinary visuals into extraordinary masterpieces!

Unleash Your Creativity with Over 200 Presets and 100 Effects

Presets offers you a vast collection of over 200 stunning presets made with Lightroom that are carefully crafted to enhance the mood and aesthetics of your photos and videos. From vibrant and punchy colors to subtle and delicate tones, there is a preset for every style and taste. With Presets, you can easily apply these presets to your photos and videos, giving them a professional and polished look.

Take Control of Your Edits with Advanced Editing Tools

Presets doesn't stop at just filters and effects. It also provides you with a comprehensive set of advanced editing tools to fine-tune your visuals to perfection. Whether you want to adjust the brightness, contrast, saturation, or even apply selective edits, Presets has got you covered. With its intuitive interface, you can effortlessly navigate through the editing options and make precise adjustments.

Revolutionary Video Editing Features

In addition to its photo editing capabilities, Presets also offers powerful video editing features. With just a few taps, you can trim, crop, or rotate your videos to achieve the desired composition. Apply stunning filters and effects to add a cinematic touch to your videos. Whether you want to create a slow-motion effect or add dynamic transitions, Presets has the tools you need to bring your videos to life.

The Ultimate Photo and Video Editor in One App

Presets combines the functionality of a powerful photo editor and a versatile video editor in one convenient app. Whether you're a professional photographer, a social media influencer, or just someone who wants to make their visuals stand out, Presets has the tools and features to meet your needs. Enhance your photos with a wide range of filters, adjust the lighting and colors with precision, and add stunning effects to create a unique visual style. Edit your videos with ease, trim and combine clips, apply transitions and effects, and even add music to bring your videos to life.

Presets: Elevate Your Visuals to New Heights

With its extensive collection of presets that were made with Lightroom, effects, and advanced editing tools, this app is the ultimate app for anyone passionate about visual storytelling. Whether you're a professional photographer, an aspiring content creator, or simply someone who loves capturing moments, Presets will take your photos and videos to new heights.

Each preset in Presets app is designed to enhance and transform your visuals with professional-grade edits. Whether you want to achieve a vintage film look, create a moody atmosphere, or enhance vibrant and punchy colors, the Lightroom inspired presets in Presets app have got you covered.

Get unlimited full access to all Presets. Enjoy an advanced editing toolkit with a wide array of adjustments. No boundaries for your creativity.

Presets Pro is available as a subscription. Prices may vary depending on your country of residence and may be converted to your local currency. Your subscription will automatically renew and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. You can turn off the auto-renewal at any time in your iTunes account settings but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of a subscription period.

Terms of use: https://presets.app/terms-of-use

Privacy policy: https://presets.app/privacy-policy

If you have any questions, concerns, feedback, or just want to chat, hit us up: support@presets.app

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Sometimes, when you're busy squashing bugs, a few sneak by. We've fixed more in this update.

We hope you enjoy using the latest version of our application. As always, please let us know if you have any feedback or suggestions for future releases. If you have any questions, don't hesitate to contact us via email at support@presets.app

apps.title: Secret Photo Album - SA
apps.description:
Protect your photos and videos by hiding them in a secret folder!

Secret Album offers great features like:
– Secure cloud backup
– Unlimited storage
– Private browser with ad blocker
– Break-in alerts
– Fake PIN

Hide photos and videos in a secret vault and keep them away from nosy folks when they are using your device.

Secret Album will keep your files in the encrypted, PIN-protected storage that only you can access. Now you can be sure that your personal data is safely hidden. Additionally, the app features a private browser with a built-in ad blocker, ensuring a seamless, secure, and distraction-free browsing experience without leaving any traces behind.

Take pictures with the in-app Secret Album camera or import images from Photos to your secret space. Use encrypted cloud storage to access your private album from different devices. Your friends and family will only see what is in the easily accessible Photos app, not in your private photo vault.

Secret Album is a secure media storage that offers:
* PIN,Touch and Face ID access to your secure files
* Decoy PIN to hide real photos and videos
* Break-in alerts and security reports with intruders' photos
* Private browser to surf securely
* Ad blocker for an uninterrupted browsing experience
* Custom color themes and album covers
* App lock after 3 incorrect PINs to prevent password cracking
* Media player with full-screen support
* Separate PIN to protect selected albums
* Built-in camera to take pictures within the app
* App content cover for the multitasking mode
* Recovery of removed photos and videos
* Slideshow support
* Full support of iOS 15 and later versions

Secure Cloud Storage:
The Premium version offers unlimited cloud storage, allowing your device to access your photos and videos any time using your email. To sync photos and videos between devices and easily restore your data in case your device gets broken or lost, you'll register your email in the app Settings.

– Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. The cost depends on the selected plan
– Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase
– Any unused portion of the free trial will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription

apps.title: Photo Collage Montage Maker
apps.description:
Quickly combine multiple photos into one beautifully framed picture. Join over 3 million users who love to tell their story and share with friends & family via social media or email! Also great for printing!

Choose your pictures and the app automatically frames them in multiple ways - so easy! Pick your preferred collage and share. You will love the endless combinations of patterns, stickers, text, borders, filters, shapes, frames and more.

Create a before-and-after sequence, combine up to 20 great photos of each of your kids, or produce a photographic series. Also super useful for online businesses to display product!

Perfect for capturing and sharing celebrations, holidays, pets, culinary achievements and more. Your friends will love the beautiful collages you produce. So much more personal than simply posting individual photos.

Here's how it works:
• Select your photos and watch as they are automatically put into multiple collages
• Choose the collage arrangement you like best
• Select your colors or background patterns
• Add text and stickers
• Save to Camera Roll or share your masterpiece on your favorite social media networks including Facebook, Twitter and Instagram.

Here's what some of our users had to say:
****
This is the most awesome app in the world!! Especially for a die hard scrapbooker who doesn't have time to do traditional scrapbooking any more. Love, love, love this app!

There are endless ways to utilize this App! So much fun! It lets me be creative! Great job!

Hands down, this is my favorite collage app... And believe me, I've tried many!!
****

FEATURES

• COMBINE YOUR PHOTOS INTO A UNIQUE COLLAGE
  - Over 120 layouts - All layouts are FREE!!!
  - Over 90 Free beautiful pattern backgrounds + Unsplash and Pixababy
  - Over 40 Free stickers
  - Over 50 Pro pattern backgrounds
  - Amazing photo effects to apply to individual photos
  - Easy share direct to Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, Flikr, Tumblr, Email
  - Save to Camera Roll

• CAPTION & STYLE YOUR PIC & COLLAGE
  - Add text easily and quickly
  - 61 creative fonts
  - Easy to change text color, size, font, background
  - Easy to move, resize and rotate the text

• EDIT PIC & COLLAGE WITH PRO PHOTO EDITOR
  - Edit photo via a built-in PRO photo editor
  - Zoom in grid to pan, pinch, rotate photo
  - Pan, rotate or mirror each photo
  - Rounded corners on photos
  - Move photos between different grids by drag and drop
  - Tap picture to show photo edit menu
  - Shadow each photo

apps.title: BeReal: Photos & Friends Daily
apps.description:
BeReal is the simplest photo-sharing app where you and your friends post once a day to show what you’re really up to.

Every day at a random time, everyone gets the same two-minute window to take and share a photo. The camera snaps both the front and back simultaneously, capturing the real moment. No filters — just real life, as it happens.

You won’t find influencers here. You’ll find your friends making coffee, walking to class, lying on the floor, laughing at nothing, or stuck in traffic. It’s not about looking perfect. It’s about being present and staying connected in a way that’s honest, unfiltered, and sometimes unintentionally hilarious.

Post on time or post late—it still counts. Comment, react with your face using RealMojis, or just scroll through your circle’s day. Your BeReal feed is private by default, unless you choose to go public and see what others are up to around the world.

If you’re tired of chasing clout and scrolling endless edits, BeReal is your once-a-day reset. One daily notification. Two minutes. Real friends, real moments.

Download BeReal and join the social network that’s not trying to be one.

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References
raw_data.releaseNotes:
We’ve been busy behind the scenes, making sure your BeReal experience is as smooth and authentic as it should be.

Here’s what we’ve done:
Squashed pesky bugs, so nothing gets in the way of your real moments.
Fine-tuned your favorite app, so everything feels as smooth as your best BeReal moments.

Update now, and keep being your naturally awesome self on BeReal. We’ve got the tech covered — you just keep being real.

— The BeReal Team

apps.title: PicMix Lite
apps.description:
Blend your photos together into an amazing work of art!

With this app you have complete freedom over which parts of the photos you want to keep. You can remove (or re-add) parts of the images with your fingers, like painting. Change the settings of the brush for fine-tuning. With this technique you can create montages, replace backgrounds or combine pictures any possible way you can imagine. You can also create semi-transparent layers of photos.

Multi-layer support to manipulate multiple layers separately, similar to professional desktop photo editing applications. Color-sensitive brush follows the edges automatically when cutting out shapes.

You can also store the cutouts you made, so they can be reused for different montages.

With this lite version you can not save pictures larger than 600 pixels.

JOIN MILLIONS OF HAPPY USERS

apps.title: Same Day Prints: Quick Photos
apps.description:
Print from your Phone, Pick up at Walgreens Photo Partner, CVS, and Duane Reade!

Introducing the one-stop solution for your photo printing needs - Same Day Prints! With this amazing app, you can now print your favorite photos directly from your phone and pick them up in just one hour at over 16,000 retailers nationwide. Whether you need prints for your scrapbook, photo album, or just to decorate your wall, Same Day Prints can make the process quick and easy.

The app is incredibly user-friendly, with an intuitive interface that makes it easy to select your photos, choose your print size, crop and adjust the images, and place your order. Print and create with photos on your phone.  Choose from many pre-designed cards and create a last minute gift, ready in just 1 hour at a store near you.

With Same Day Prints, you can rest assured that your prints will be of the highest quality, with vibrant colors, sharp details, and excellent clarity. Plus, you can choose from a variety of pickup locations, including CVS, Walgreens Photo Partner, and Duane Reade, making it convenient to get your prints wherever and whenever you need them.

So why wait? Download Same Day Prints today and start printing your favorite photos in no time!




Products vary by location please refer to the lists below --
PHOTO PRODUCTS VARY BY STORE

- CVS -
Photo Prints: 4x6, 5x5, 5x7, 6x6, 6x8, 8x8 8x10 prints. 2x3 wallet prints
Photo Print Enlargements and Posters: 11x14, 16x20, 20x24, 24x36
Photo Mugs: 11 and 15 oz Photo mug
Metallic Prints: 11x14, 12x16, 12x18, 16x20, 18x24, 20x24, 20x30, 24x36
Greeting Cards: 4x8 photo greeting cards or holiday cards
Canvas Prints: 5x7, 8x8, 8x10, 11x14, 16x20 Canvas photo prints, 11x14 Framed Canvas
Board Prints: 11x14,16x20 Board Prints
Mounted Photo Panels: 4x6, 6x8, 8x10 photo panels, 8x10 acrylic panel
Bamboo Photo Panels: 8x10 Bamboo Panel
Hanging Canvas: 11x14 Hanging Canvas Print
Magnets: 4x6 Photo Magnet
Photo Books: 4x6 photo book (10 photos), 8.5x11 Layflat Photo Book
Wall Tides: 8x8 Wall Tile Photo Prints
Photo Collages: 5x7, 8x10 Multi Layout Collage Photo Prints
Acrylic Collage Panel: 8x10 Multi Layout Acrylic Collage Panel
Bamboo Collage: 8x10 Multi Layout Acrylic Collage Panel
Other Photo Gifts: Double-sided (2x2) bamboo ornament, 2x2 Cube Ornament, 3x3 Photo cube, 11x13 Photo Puzzle, Tumbler, Can Cooler

- Walgreens Photo Partner -
Photo Prints: 4x4, 4x6, 5x5, 5x7, 8x8, 8x10 prints
Holiday Cards: 4x8 Holiday Cars (Set of 20)
Photo Canvas: 8x10, 11x14, 12x12, 16x20 photo wrapped canvas
Enlargements: 11x14, 16x20, 20x30, 24x36 Enlargements/Poster
Wood Panel: 5x7, 8x10 wood panel photo prints
Metal Panel: 11x14 Metal Panel Prints
Board Prints: 11x14, 16x20 and 20x30 Board Prints
Mouse pad, Photo Puzzles


HOW TO PRINT
1. Start by downloading our Same Day Prints app to your iPhone.
2. After downloading open the app and choose between CVS, Walgreens Photo Partner, or Home Delivery.
3. Select the product you’d like to print. Products vary depending on your chosen retail store (refer to the list above).
4. Upload photos from your camera roll to our app. Once uploaded, choose which photo you want to print. When selected a green check mark appears on the bottom right corner.
5. You can choose your desired dimensions and quantity by selecting the red box down below.
6. After you add your selected product to the cart, tap “find your store” and select you’re the best store in proximity to your location.
7. Enter your name, email, and phone number and review your order. No Credit Card Necessary. (Credit Card or PayPal need in case of Home delivery.)
8. Once your order is placed, you will receive an email in less than 1 hour letting you know your order is ready!
9. Pay when you review your photos at the store you selected and enjoy the rest of your day!

apps.title: Once Upon | Photo book Creator
apps.description:
Over 7,600,000 photo fans can’t be wrong – make fantastic photo books and photo prints easily, right from your phone with Once Upon. Create several books and prints simultaneously, and work on them when it suits you. Combining your special moments in a personal, designed book has never been easier. In just a few minutes, you’ll let your pictures live beyond your phone. Do it on the go, or when relaxing at home. 

How Once Upon works:
- Choose up to 594 images from your phone, tablet or computer
- Write a few captions (optional) 
- Select from several pre-designed layout alternatives
- Repeat as many times as you wish! One book holds up to 200 pages

OUR PHOTO BOOKS
You select the format of your book once you’ve created your content. We have three alternative formats: Softcover Medium, Hardcover Medium and Hardcover Large. You can also choose to go with glossy or silk matte paper. 

Softcover Medium, 8x8"
Hardcover Medium, 8x8", album title printed on spine
Hardcover Large, 11x11", album title printed on spine

OUR PHOTO PRINTS
Get started on a collection made of high-quality paper you’ll definitely want to keep. Our prints are available in the 5x7” size, and you can choose to make them in matte or semi-gloss paper. The format will adjust to either landscape or portrait depending on your photo. 

OUR FEATURES
- Collaborative albums – invite as many friends as you like
- Shuffle function to highlight your favorite layout
- Captions let you say a little something about every memory
- Drag-and-drop to arrange your pages in no time
- Copy spreads between your albums to keep multiple versions simple
- Easy image selection with dates sorted by month
- Google Photos connection and automatic iCloud sync
- Storage – we back your images and photo books up to our servers
- Scandinavian design
- Our photo books and photo prints are printed in Australia, Germany, the Netherlands, Sweden, the UK and the USA

Questions, or just want to say hi? Grab us at happytohelp@onceupon.se.
Get inspired by fellow photo book fans via our Instagram, @onceuponapp.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
You didn't miss this, did you? 
You can now make photo books and photo prints from your phone or tablet and through your computer's web browser.

Plus, in this version of the app, we got rid of a few bugs to help you create seamlessly.

apps.title: Amazon Photos: Photo & Video
apps.description:
Use this free app to back up, share, and organize your photos and videos. All Amazon Photos customers have 5GB full-resolution photo and video storage. Prime members have unlimited photo storage (available only in the US, UK, CA, DE, FR, IT, ES and JP) and 5GB for video. 

Personalize your Fire TV and Echo Show to display your favorite memories. Order photo prints, custom gifts, and home décor directly from your phone to make gift giving a breeze (available in the US only). You can opt to remove photos and videos stored in your phone to free up space, knowing your photos and videos will remain safe—now and in the future. Safely store all your full-resolution photos on Amazon Photos. 

FULL-RESOLUTION STORAGE
Amazon Photos keeps your photos and videos the same size and format as the originals. With full-resolution storage, your prints look as sharp as the day you took them. More pixels equal better-quality photos and videos.

PERSONALIZE YOUR FIRE TV AND ECHO SHOW
So many photos and videos captured remain tucked away in a phone or camera. Device personalization means your best memories stay where they belong: in the spotlight. Whether it’s your Fire TV in the living room or your Echo Show on the kitchen counter, your memories get the attention they deserve.

THIS DAY
View (and share) photos from this date in years past, whether it’s one year ago or five years ago. 


MEMORIES
Your special moments set to music and re-surfaced as a curated slideshow to re-live the good times. 


SHARING
Share full-resolution photos and videos with family and friends by inviting them to a private Amazon Photos Group. Share lifetime-long memories or highlight special events such as vacations, playoffs, parties, graduations. View photo slideshows on your Fire TV and Echo Show to enjoy special moments throughout your entire home. 

PRINTS
High-quality prints, made to order. Best of all? You can make it happen right from the app and transform those memories into prints, custom gifts, and home décor. Available only in the U.S. 

AUTO-SAVE
Back up photos and videos automatically just by turning on with Auto-Save.

ALEXA
Take, view, and share photos hands-free.

GROUPS
Privately share selected photos, videos, and albums with family and friends across devices. 

SUBSCRIPTIONS
Expand storage with flexible monthly and annual plans starting at $1.99

By using this app, you agree to Amazon’s Conditions of Use (www.amazon.com/conditionsofuse) and Privacy Notice (www.amazon.com/privacy).

apps.description:
Trying to recover your lost or deleted photos? PicRestore gives you easy access to recover any important photos or videos that you might have lost or deleted.

◆ How to use the PicRestore App ◆ 

● Recover deleted photos and videos in a single tap

● PicRestore allows you to filter through your entire camera roll to locate and recover the photos and videos that you've previously lost or deleted


—————————————————————————————————


PicRestore subscription policy:

Once you sign up to PicRestore Premium, you will have full access to all of PicRestore's features for free for 3 days.

You can cancel your subscription any time and you will be sent a reminder before your PicRestore subscription begins after your trial.

PicRestore Premium Subscription:

- With a PicRestore Premium subscription you have access to recover your lost photos, delete duplicate photos and contacts, find and remove large photos and videos, and store private photos and videos in the private vault section.
- PicRestore Premium weekly subscription is billed weekly for $2.99, and payment will be charged to iTunes Account after a 30 day free trial.
- Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.
- Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal.
- Subscriptions can be managed by the user and auto-renewal can be turned off by going to the user's iPhone Settings -> Apple ID -> Subscriptions.


—————————————————————————————————

apps.title: SimplePrints Photo Books
apps.description:
Transform your phone's images into special custom photo gifts or beautiful wall art! We made creating photo books, canvas prints, metal prints, and other photo products so quick and easy that anyone can do it. Our goal is to build an app that helps celebrate your favorite memories. Select the moments that make you smile and bring them to life with photo prints in a few simple steps.

What we offer 

Photo Books
- 8x8 softcover, 8x8 hardcover, or 12x12 hardcover
- Paper types: Standard, Premium, and Photo Lustre
- Photo captions 
- Collage layouts
- Spine text on hardcovers
- Photo Filters
- Dedication page
- Customize cover design  
- Customize back cover 
- Virtual book to share for free

Layflat Photo Books
- 8”x8” hardcover or 12”x12” hardcover 
- Panoramic and gutter-less experience
- Photo captions 
- Collage layouts
- Spine text
- Photo Filters
- Customize cover design  
- Customize back cover 
- Virtual book to share

Mini Photo Books 
- 3.5" x 3.5" books come in sets of 3
- Photo captions 
- Collage layouts
- Photo Filters
- Customize cover design  
- Virtual book to share

Canvas Prints
- 5 sizes - 8”x10”, 11”x14”, 16”x20”, 16”x24”, 24”x36”
- Gallery wrapped 
- Photo Filters
- Collage layouts
- Colored borders 
- Wall Mount included 
- 360 preview of the final product

Metal Prints
- 6 sizes - 8”x10”, 11”x14”, 12”x18”, 16”x20”, 16”x24”, 24”x36”
- Photo Filters
- Collage layouts
- Colored borders 
- Wall Mount included 
- 360 preview of the final product

Wall Calendars 
- 8.5”x11” with white spiral binding 
- Choose starting month
- Collage layouts
- Photo Filters
- Colored borders 

We are focused on providing quality prints and will provide lifetime support for your projects when you need it.The best part is that our photo products are made with love in the United States and available internationally. Our fantastic customer service team is standing by to make sure you are happy with your order.

“There’s nothing like seeing my work come to life in print. SimplePrints has made it easier than ever to order and customize photo products straight from your phone. Such amazing quality and quick turnaround! I ordered this photobook and canvas prints to gift to my clients and they absolutely loved it!” - Celebrity Photographer, Patty, Othon

“SimplePrints is great for those who do not want to spend weeks on editing books and don’t want to suffocate in options. It is very, very simple and you get a great quality book in the end. It’s for those who take photos daily but never develop them or organize them.” - Photo Book Guru

Frequently Asked Questions

Do I have to pay to install the app or is there a membership fee?
- Downloading the app is free and you do not need to pay a membership fee. Create an account with confidence and only pay for the photo products you want to buy. 

How much do Photo Books cost?
- Our Photo Books start at $14.99 and our virtual photo books are free. 

Can text be added to photo books?
- Yes! You can add captions to your pages, a title on the cover, spine text on hardcover books, and we offer a text only dedication page (except for Layflat photo books).

Can I upload my own photos?
- Yes you can. You can import photos from your phone gallery, dropbox, google photos, Instagram, and Facebook. 

How do I get started?
- Download our app, create a free account, select between our photo books, wall prints, or other photo products you want from the catalog, import your photos, make any customizations you desire, and submit your order. 

What is the turnaround time?
- Once you submit your order, products may take 5 - 10 business days to arrive. Please note, deliveries outside of the US may take longer. Please check the app for our most up to date delivery estimates. 

Does SimplePrints ship outside of the US?
- Yes we do! Please check our app for country specific information.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
New Photo Book features!
- You can now add custom text stickers and place them anywhere on your project for a personalized touch!
- The front and back covers are now larger on the Edit Book screen, improving visibility and enhancing your editing experience.
Overall Maintenance
- Bug fixes and general performance improvements.

Our team is constantly working to bring you the best products and app experience. We are on standby to help you with any questions, feedback, or issues. Please email us at hello@simpleprints.com. We'd love to hear from you!

The NewProfilePic app lets you change your user image style as often as you want. Dare to be different, with a profile pic that reflects your current mood or state of mind. Impress your friends on social media and keep them interested in what's coming next! ;)

apps.title: Clip2Comic: Cartoon Yourself
apps.description:
Clip2Comic is a high-quality, high-resolution picture editing app that transforms your photos into funny cartoons, caricatures and sketches in a matter of seconds directly on your Mac, iPhone or iPad. You prefer videos? Create your own cartoon and comic clips with our live preview camera, or make a cartoon out of an existing video with only one tap.

Use Clip2Comic for free!
- 9 brand new styles! Enhance your images with the trendiest and most iconic comic styles.
- Transform as many photos and videos as you like into cartoon, poster and sketch art
- See the world as a cartoon using the cartoon camera with live preview
- Apply all cartoon art effects instantly on your Mac, iPhone or iPad
- Save your comic, poster, sketch or caricature in high-resolution, videos up to 4K and 60FPS and images up to 64MP

As a plus, Clip2Comic Premium** gives you the opportunity to experiment with a new kind of editing tool: With your finger or Apple Pencil you will be able to remove unwanted outlines, make strokes smaller or thicker, or even remove the original colors from your cartoonized photos. This way you are able to retouch a face in a portrait or to even create coloring pages! Try the deformation tool to caricature your artwork even better, e.g., to create a funny face. Refine, reshape or bloat parts of your picture. It's easier than ever. Last but not least, make your cartoons special with Clip2Comic's color filters or poster styles.

Share your cartoon or surprise your friends and family with a print. We work together with www.mypostcard.com to offer an integrated postcard service. They will send your awesome results as a real postcard for only $2.69, including free shipping! Keep in touch with your friends and family all over the world in a fun and easy way. Surprise them with a postcard to any occasion. We've also teamed up with CanvasPop to offer a printing service with a 100% "Love it" guarantee. Have your favorite cartoonized moment printed on canvas or as a poster and delivered straight to your door. Even large sizes are not a problem thanks to our high-quality, high-resolution technology.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
- Select a photo or video from your library
- Catch a special moment directly as a cartoon by using the cartoon camera with live preview
- Choose between various comic, poster, sketch and caricature effects
- Adjust outlines, details and the blackness of your picture**
- Select a color for your poster effect and decide on the color amount**
- Retouch a cartoonized face, portrait or even landscapes with your finger or Apple Pencil**
- Deformation tools help you to create stunning caricatures**
- Set your cartoons in the right mood with color filters**
- Save your comic, poster, sketch or caricature in high-resolution, videos up to 4K and 60FPS and images up to 64MP
- With Custom Styles you can personalize and save your very own styles with ease. 
- Share your art on social media like TikTok, Instagram, YouTube, Snapchat and Facebook
- Print your results with our integrated printing services, e.g., order a postcard for just $2.69 (free shipping included!)

Dive into a comic world you created yourself—with Clip2Comic. 

Download the app FOR FREE now! 

SUPPORT
If you have any questions or feedback for us, please feel free to send us an email at support@digitalmasterpieces.com. Our team is on hand 24 hours a day, so we'll get right on it.

Optimized for OS 26, the iPhone 17 and iPhone 17 Pro.

** Subscribe to unlock all features. 
Terms of Use: https://www.digitalmasterpieces.com/app-terms-of-use/

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Embark on your artistic journey as you discover the best and most stunning filters with Clip2Comic! 

OS 26 and UI improvements
We’ve updated the app to run smoothly on the latest operating systems. You’ll notice better performance and improved stability. We also introduce a new fresh look with Liquid Glass. Several screens now feature the new Liquid Glass UI, giving your artwork more space and a cleaner editing experience.

Improved Zoom & Canvas Placement
We’ve redesigned the zoom view, so your canvas is easier to position — no more sliders getting in the way of your edits!

Comic Panels
Elevate your artwork with professionally curated digital panel styles, perfect for showcasing your creations in a virtual gallery, capturing attention on social media, or adding the final touch to your masterpiece. Explore a handpicked collection designed for perfect comic panel aesthetics.

More Precision and Control
We've refined all sliders for better control and understandability. You can now see exact values and reset them easily—just double-tap the slider or tap the default value. The signature tool has also been improved, allowing you to move, rotate, and scale your signature freely with touch gestures.

Dynamic Comic Effects
Give your edits extra flair with new decorations! Add authentic comic speed lines or playful cartoon clouds, then customize their style to match your vision.

Custom Signatures

Plus, seamless Finder and file-system integration makes loading and saving images a breeze.

Produce fun, original images in seconds with Image Playground directly on your device. Create entirely new images based on descriptions, with suggested concepts and styles such as illustration and animation. Use our app to turn your creations into high-quality art effortlessly. 


The latest version contains bug fixes and performance improvements.

apps.title: Avatan – Photo Editor
apps.description:
Avatan is a social photo editor.

It enables people to edit photos interacting with each other, while using their own processing elements.
All the elements are created and added by users to the social network integrated with the photo editor.

EFFECTS
You have the opportunity to create and save your own, customized effects.
To create effects, you can use various tools and resources.

RESOURCES
You can add and use 4 various resources when editing images:
* Stickers
* Textures
* Frames
* Backgrounds

RETOUCHING
Moreover, the photo editor features embedded functions for all the necessary types of face retouching and body shape adjustment. This makes it possible to always easily eliminate any imperfections with high quality.

You can save your favorite effects and resources to apply them later while editing your new photos. Due to these multiple options, your edited photos will always be of high quality and special style. Every second an enormous number of users add new effects and resources for editing images on a variety of themes, replenishing their collections. Thus, the range of opportunities offered by the photo editor is constantly growing. The intuitive and convenient interface makes it possible to implement complex processing in simple steps. The entire process is a pure joy.

We offer in-app purchases for Premium, which includes unlimited amount of adding elements to favourites and other features. The amount will be charged to your iTunes account and will vary by plan and country. You’ll see the total price before completing payment.

Premium subscriptions purchased in-app renew monthly or yearly depending on your plan. To  avoid renewal, you must turn off auto-renew at least 24 hours before your subscription ends. You can turn off auto-renew at any time from iTunes account settings.

Also we offer in-app purchase Premium One-time. The payment process just one time. After that You get Premium features once for all without other payments. If You have an active Premium subscription and want to get Premium One-time, You need to turn off auto-renew at least 24 hours before your subscription ends. After subscription ends You can buy Premium One-time.

Terms of Use: https://avatanplus.ru/pages/eula
Privacy Policy: https://avatanplus.ru/pages/privacy-en

apps.title: RetroFix - Old Picture Restore
apps.description:
Transform old photos into clear, vibrant memories with RetroFix! This AI-powered photo restoration app makes it easy to enhance, restore, and clean up old photos, so your cherished images look like new again.

RetroFix is the ultimate app for old photo restoration on iPhone, perfect for bringing life back to faded, damaged, or black-and-white photos. Whether you want to remove scratches, repair damaged images, or make old photos clear, RetroFix has all the tools you need.

【Key Features】

• AI-Powered Restoration: RetroFix’s advanced AI can make old photos clear by removing blur, restoring photo quality, and enhancing image clarity. Ideal for photo repair, it’s the best app to fix old pictures and revive old photos instantly.

• Old Photo Colorizer: Make old black-and-white photos come to life with realistic colors! Our app is the ultimate tool for adding vibrant hues to faded images.

• Repair and Enhance: Fix underexposed photos, adjust lighting, and enhance sharpness effortlessly. RetroFix improves photo quality with ease, making your memories fresh and clear.

• Scratch & Damage Repair: Remove scratches, discoloration, and years of wear from old photos. RetroFix is your go-to app to repair damaged photos and renew old memories.

【Why Choose RetroFix?】

• Comprehensive Restoration Solution: RetroFix specializes in making old photos clear and restoring their original beauty. From minor adjustments to full restorations, it’s the best app to fix old photos on iPhone.

• User-Friendly & Fast: RetroFix offers powerful photo restoration tools that anyone can use, making it the best app to restore old photos on iPhone.

• Instant Results: See your photos transform in seconds! With easy comparisons, RetroFix is perfect for clearing up old photos and bringing them back to life.

Rediscover and restore your memories effortlessly with RetroFix. From cleaning up old photos to enhancing photo quality, RetroFix is the all-in-one app to restore and revive old pictures. Download now and see how RetroFix can make your memories new again!

For subscriptions, we follow the standard Apple Terms of Use (https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/).

raw_data.releaseNotes: This update brings a few important bug fixes and performance improvements to make RetroFix faster and more reliable. Enjoy smoother photo restoration, quicker colorization, and a better overall experience as you bring your old memories back to life!

apps.title: Touchpix · Photo & Video Booth
apps.description:
Touchpix is the 360 photo booth, video booth, and photo booth app software solution for event professionals. 

FEATURES
- GoPro 7,8,9,10,11, 12 and 13 support
- Wired GoPro connection 
- Nikon and Canon DSLR support
- Revolutionary built-in internet free sharing (Scanpix)
- Powerful video effects creator (modify settings and video effects from desktop or mobile)
- Real-time sync for instant updates across all devices
- Still photos, boomerang gifs, video, burst gifs, slow motion video
- Full customizable UI
- Customizable emails with HTML and CSS for a more branded experience 
- Included themes for fun personalization
- Use 16 photo templates and 7 video, boomerang, slow motion, gif templates
- Add face props for extra fun
- Add filters and effects
- AI effects
- Draw on photos
- Add text to photos
- Add 'stickers' to photos
- Sharing via email, QR, SMS, Whatsapp, Facebook, Twitter, and download
- Scan ’n go unique sharing system
- Sharing works offline using queuing
- Use the app as sharing station 
- Automatic background removal (greenscreen'less' green screen)
- Show the session on a TV using Airplay
- Show the slideshow on a TV using Airplay
- Download files from TV with a QR code
- Trigger session by movement or a face
And much more

EVENTS
Manage your events and templates in your online account
Branded online gallery and event data available after the event for sharing

IN-APP PURCHASES
With the 'professional' in-app purchase, you can activate unlimited events during a week, month or year, depending on the chosen package. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period is not allowed. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal can be turned off in your Account Settings in iTunes after purchase. For the subscription, you have three options: 1. Weekly professional 2. Monthly professional 3. Yearly professional. 

Privacy statement: https://touchpix.com/privacy-statement-touchpix/
General terms: https://touchpix.com/general-terms-and-conditions-of-touchpix/

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Gallery performance optimized — smoother browsing, even with large numbers of files.

Faster sharing — improved speed when sharing via email, SMS, or WhatsApp, especially after the first share.

Camera stability improved — resolved an issue that could cause the camera on iPads to freeze or return to the main screen.

apps.title: PopPic - 3D Photo Camera
apps.description:
PopPic lets you take amazing 3D photos that you can view and share with friends and family.

PopPic works just like a normal camera, but instead of taking flat photos, it also captures an extra dimension: depth.

Photos taken with PopPic can be explored in 3D. Tilt your phone to change your viewpoint. Pinch to move toward and away from the subject. Add depth effects and motion to bring your photos to life. Share your creations with friends and family on Instagram, Facebook, or Snapchat, or save them to your camera roll.

FEATURES:
* Take 3D photos that you can explore by rotating your phone.
* Adjust focus and depth of field after taking the photo.
* Get creative with depth effects and filters.
* Add motion to bring your photos to life.
* Share your 3D photos with friends.
* Import photos from your camera roll and view them in 3D.


WHAT PEOPLE ARE SAYING ABOUT POPPIC:
Over 20,000 people have given PopPic a perfect 5-star rating on the App Store. Here's what a few of them had to say:

"This is a stunning app. It does things that are so unique and so awesome" -Keywiz
"I love it, takes beautiful pics." -Boogie724
"Simply Enjoyable & Fun" -gordie06
"Absolutely flawless." -OxfordLawn


POP PIC PRO:
PopPic Pro is an upgrade to unlock our complete collection of over 40 filters and effects, new types of custom motion, HD video output, and sharing without a PopPic watermark.

PopPic Pro is available as a one-time purchase or monthly subscription with free trial.

We think you’ll love PopPic Pro, but even if you choose not to upgrade, you can still take, view, and share as many 3D photos as you like, and a number of our filters and depth effects will be free forever.


ADDITIONAL INFORMATION:
Visit our Website: https://poppic.cam
Terms of Service: https://poppic.cam/about/terms
Privacy Policy: https://poppic.cam/about/privacy
Music: "Dreams" by bensound.com

Revive is an AI video maker that offers a handpicked selection of photo animations, funny filters, trendy beats, and ai video effects for your pictures. Animate photos and transform your images to video with our AI video generator. Sing like Marilyn Monroe, Queen, Rihanna, and more.

- Make photo dance with trendy beats

- Create funny video with a gender swap filter
- Animate photos realistically —  add wind, explosions, gestures, and fire to bring your stories into motion. 

Face Animation & Talking Photo

apps.title: WiFi Photo Transfer
apps.description:
Easily access your photo libraries via wifi from any computer with a web browser! 

Just start the app and enter the displayed address into the address bar of your browser. Works with any computer that has a modern browser (like desktop or portable computers, iPads, or even an other iPhone) and is on the same wifi network as your phone, iPod or iPad. 


- You can select and transfer multiple photos at once
- EXIF metadata is retained in mass-download mode (not in one-by-one mode)
- Optional password protection for the web interface
- Can also be used to download videos
- Transfer in full resolution or scaled down
- No extra software required


It's simple yet useful. And it's free.

raw_data.releaseNotes: hopefully the last of the iOS 13 related bugfixes: reencoding pictures to JPEG did not work for some people, this update fixes that.

apps.title: yope: only best friends pics
apps.description:
yope is the friends-only photo sharing app
It’s the safest, simplest way to stay close. Share real photos with your closest circle — they appear instantly on friends’ lock screens and widgets.

On Instagram, you’re performing. On Yope, you’re just living.

We made Yope because social media became too fake. Filters, edits, likes — all noise.
Yope is different. No audience. No pressure. Just you and the people you actually care about.

why people switch to yope

• private by design – only your friends see your photos
• surprise lockscreen updates – stay connected without opening the app
• widget on your homescreen – daily moments in one glance
• fast, easy photo sharing – one tap, no edits, no stress
• built-in photo chats – skip the texting, share visually
• different groups, different energy – show your real self in every circle
• streaks that make friendships stronger – post together, grow together

real people. real photos. no performance.
Share what matters. See the moments that do.
No likes. No rankings. No stress. Just real updates — from people you love.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
another big one you’ve been asking for: live photos are here!
now you can snap the moment with all the vibes — moving, real, full of energy. just you + your besties + the feels
